cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_PORT_FOR_S1U to 0 will cause connection failure as port 0 is invalid and cannot be used for network communication.

du.explanation_en: Setting GNB_PORT_FOR_S1U to 0 will cause connection failure as port 0 is invalid and cannot be used for network communication.
du.explanation_zh: 將 GNB_PORT_FOR_S1U 設定為 0 會導致連接失敗，因為端口 0 無效，無法用於網路通訊。
